Page_0: "Dronen, that weasel Finkle is working late again tonight. After he leaves I want you to run by the security room and make sure he remembered to leave the Mech security cameras on. Idiot keeps trying to cut costs by shutting them off after hours. Come by and I'll give you the key. I'll be standing watch tonight up on the second floor, just outside of the storage area at the top of the stairs.
Captain Cassagrande"